title = "Claim:  Storm or flood"
content = "✅ What's covered:
Storm:
Your insurer will cover loss or damage caused by storm.
❌ What isn’t covered:
Loss or damage:
• Caused by subsidence, heave or landslip resulting from storm
or flood
• Caused by frost"
